  <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">

    <h2>NeverFap Deluxe Courses</h2>

    <p>NeverFap Deluxe Courses combine the NeverFap Articles and Practices into single, linear progression-based pathways based upon The Five Fundamental Principles of NeverFap.</p>
    <p>They are designed to help you focus on a particular area of understanding, so that you can master that concept and feel confident with your ability to address your porn addiction.</p>
    <p>As mentioned earlier, I recommend getting started with the Introduction course and working your way down the list, revisiting practices you personally found useful.</p>
    <p>In addition, these courses will also be available as premium audio courses if you decide to <a class="link" href="/accounts">sign up</a> with a NeverFap Deluxe Community account. (although they don't yet exist, so stay tuned!)</p>

  </div>
</div>

<%= partial "links/custom.html", %{ title: "Courses", text: "Check out our NeverFap Deluxe Courses!", link: "/courses" } %>

